result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="800"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭">
  
  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">
    
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="评论ID">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'commentid', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="用户ID">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'userid', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="点赞时间">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入点赞时间" v-decorator="['createtime', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>

    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
</a-modal>
